{"tid":155619,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"拆開中國製電話 便知抵制南韓有幾不智","createTime":"2017-03-14T07:38:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-14T09:55:11.000Z","uid":22675,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3f5c864fb5e136d59528b11eb0a76f39a742091c","tid":155619,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T07:38:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://china.hket.com/article/1700421/拆開國產手機%20便知抵制南韓有幾不智\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1700421%2F%E6%8B%86%E9%96%8B%E5%9C%8B%E7%94%A2%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%2520%E4%BE%BF%E7%9F%A5%E6%8A%B5%E5%88%B6%E5%8D%97%E9%9F%93%E6%9C%89%E5%B9%BE%E4%B8%8D%E6%99%BA&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNlzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=72fab3d2\" target=\"_blank\">http://china.hket.com/article/1700421/拆開國產手機%20便知抵制南韓有幾不智</a><br />\n中國近年屢次掀起「抵制潮」，應對與別國的政治爭端。這種抵制是否理性，其實拆掉一部國產機，便可見端倪！<br />\n<br />\n全球化的今天，一部電話的零部件可能來自五湖四海。互聯網近日就流傳一篇潮文，指拆開一部中國國產vivo Xplay6，你可發現他根本是「聯合國」製造：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1700000/1700421/1407589_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1700000%2F1700421%2F1407589_1024.jpg&h=744add4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n屏幕：三星（南韓）的5.46英寸Super AMOLED曲面顯示屏<br />\n<br />\nCPU和運存：CPU為（高通，美國）MSM8996；運存是三星K3RG6G6 0MMMGCJ運存芯片，6GB LPDDR4<br />\n<br />\n存儲：三星KLUDG8J1CB-B0B1存儲芯片，128GB UFS2.0<br />\n<br />\n鏡頭：Sony（索尼，日本）IMX362傳感器，1200萬像素<br />\n<br />\nWiFi+藍牙模塊：Qualcomm的QCA6174A<br />\n<br />\nLTE功率放大芯片：Skyworks（思佳訊，美國）77824-11<br />\n<br />\n操作系統：Google（谷歌美國）的Android 6.0.1系統<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n結論是：若要把抵制南韓、美國或日本的行動進行得徹底，首先應該告別手裏的國產機！但這樣一來，中國企業亦必然受損。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1700000/1700421/3_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1700000%2F1700421%2F3_1024.png&h=10caf152&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">國產機零部件，多是進口的。</span><br />\n<br />\n這篇文章其實是用諷刺，點出官方背後默許、甚至推波助瀾的「愛國」抵制行動，根本並非明智之舉，甚至是「殺敵一千，自損八百」。<br />\n<br />\n全球化下 抵制別人如同抵制自己<br />\n<br />\n全球化之下，各國經濟環環緊扣，利益相依，抵制別人隨時如同抵制自己。以當前被針對的南韓樂天為例，在中國僱用2萬多員工，直接和間接依靠吃飯的多達15萬人。假如抵制成功，這十多萬人的生計如何保障？這還未計中國政府可能少收的稅。<br />\n<br />\n以經濟解決政治爭端，是明智還是不智，實在不難解答。"},{"pid":"36bd716ab99239aa7f71ab5a8f94c199e545d9da","tid":155619,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T07:47:56.000Z","msg":"支持新中國義和團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n杯葛全世界<br />\n<br />\n交番個地球出黎"},{"pid":"aa9a007bf2e8efd14e0c235ef941af0503905f88","tid":155619,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T07:51:31.000Z","msg":"回到原始時代咁既生活咪可以愛國囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4113742a3eab6d948b06cfcfd1880d23cc1c41e1","tid":155619,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T07:55:39.000Z","msg":"支持鄰國人掟爛電話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48414a4011a223c3dd71a97aff71b5d4e48c8a83","tid":155619,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T08:09:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b526347150bc0ea993d47ac5ceffcdaf87645a0","tid":155619,"uid":32325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T08:13:51.000Z","msg":"集支那最憎嘅國家s於一身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eea3f15d81b4a4f46db9fa9ad5e3c9e4b90bc491","tid":155619,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T08:14:14.000Z","msg":"iFixIt 強國版 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51ba875b9f5f2bda4c5b5eac78bdbcc758f46d1e","tid":1